{"tid":112347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那外滙儲備跌穿3萬億美元   央行：2萬億夠晒","createTime":"2017-02-08T05:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T09:33:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4329b101d0d8409ffcdf67d291d27a1b75191066","tid":112347,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170208/56276096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170208%2F56276096&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0v6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=7e20e02e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170208%2F56276096&h=421a19c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170208/56276096</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170208/large/1486524751_a172.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170208%2Flarge%2F1486524751_a172.jpg&h=9db6918a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那央行主管的《金融時報》為外滙儲備跌穿3萬億美元護航，該報今日發表文章引述市場人士分析，一月份外儲下降有三個季節性因素，包括個人購滙額度恢復後增加持有外匯資產的需求、支那新年出境旅遊的購滙需求以及企業償還到期外債等。<br />\n<br />\n文章又引述專家指，若以3至6個月進口額、覆蓋100%的短期外債等通行標準衡量，支那維持1萬億美元左右的外匯儲備就足夠；<br />\n<br />\n若按國際貨幣基金組織（IMF）等機構提出的用外匯儲備與M2比率來衡量外匯儲備充足度的新方法，對於固定匯率國家，這一比率應維持在10%至20%，對於浮動匯率國家，這一比率應維持在5%至10%。<br />\n<br />\n目前支那屬於有管理的浮動匯率制，且有著較嚴格的外匯流出管理，綜合考慮，維持2萬億美元左右的外匯儲備在通常情況下可以認為是適度的。"},{"pid":"ea290392ea14dd834063427a980ea21c2a1dc6f3","tid":112347,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"留名等睇跌穿2萬億就話1萬億夠哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c25dc7949e362dbc4615502e070ee6a39f8424","tid":112347,"uid":10692,"like":0,"d